# Prefix Sum – Must-Do Questions (Minimal Set)

---

## 1. Basic Prefix Sum (Range Query)

**Problem:** [https://leetcode.com/problems/range-sum-query-immutable/](https://leetcode.com/problems/range-sum-query-immutable/)

**Pattern:** Precompute prefix array for O(1) range queries

**Core Idea:**

* pref[i] = sum of elements from 0 to i
* sum(l, r) = pref[r] - pref[l-1]

