## 2. Subarray Sum Equals K ⭐ (MOST IMPORTANT)

**Problem:** [https://leetcode.com/problems/subarray-sum-equals-k/](https://leetcode.com/problems/subarray-sum-equals-k/)

**Pattern:** Prefix Sum + HashMap

**Core Idea:**

* If (prefixSum - k) exists → valid subarray
* Use map to store frequency of prefix sums

