## 6. Contiguous Array ⭐

**Problem:** [https://leetcode.com/problems/contiguous-array/](https://leetcode.com/problems/contiguous-array/)

**Pattern:** Prefix Sum + HashMap (Transform)

**Core Idea:**

* Convert 0 → -1
* Then find longest subarray with sum = 0

