## 7. Maximum Subarray (Kadane)

**Problem:** [https://leetcode.com/problems/maximum-subarray/](https://leetcode.com/problems/maximum-subarray/)

**Pattern:** Prefix Sum Optimization

**Core Idea:**

* max subarray = current sum - minimum prefix so far
* Optimized as Kadane’s Algorithm

